f_n(x) = \frac{nx}{2 + n + x}. (0 \le x \le 1)
\lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{nx}{2 + n + x} = \lim_{n \to \infty}  \frac{x}{\frac{2}{n} + \frac{n}{n} + \frac{x}{n}} = \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{x}{0+1+0} = \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{x}{1} = \lim_{n \to \infty} x = x.
